@startuml componente
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

title Diagrama de Componentes - Top Plant

package "Frontend (React)" {
    [Interface do Usuário] as UI
    [Gerenciador de Estado/Hooks] as StateMgmt
    [Serviços de API (Axios/Fetch)] as ApiClient
}

package "Backend (Django)" {
    component "API Gateway / URLs" as Urls
    
    package "Módulos de Negócio" {
        [Componente de Cliente] as ClientComp
        [Componente de Produto] as ProductComp
        [Componente de Estoque] as StockComp
        [Componente de Pedido] as OrderComp
    }
    
    [Camada de Persistência (ORM)] as ORM
}

database "SQLite Database" as DB {
    [Tabelas de Dados] as Tables
}

' Relacionamentos Frontend
UI --> StateMgmt
StateMgmt --> ApiClient
ApiClient ..> Urls : "Requisições HTTP"

' Relacionamentos Backend
Urls --> ClientComp
Urls --> ProductComp
Urls --> StockComp
Urls --> OrderComp

ClientComp --> ORM
ProductComp --> ORM
StockComp --> ORM
OrderComp --> ORM

ORM --> Tables : "Consultas SQL"

note top of UI : Interface responsiva construída\ncom React e Tailwind CSS.
note bottom of ORM : Django ORM abstrai o acesso\nao banco de dados SQLite.

@enduml
